o other persons, a male and female were trapped with serious injuries in the Mercedes and needed to be extracted by emergency staff before being rushed to hospital,’’ said Beetge. Meanwhile , three people died after the vehicle in which they were travelling from Dysselsdorp, tried crossing the N12 and landed on a train line which runs parallel to the road.All three were declared dead on the scene. In a three-car collision just outside Oudtshoorn, one male died and two other people were left seriously injured. The accident happened on Saturday night.On the N2 at Borcherds Quarry, a pedestrian was knocked down and killed late on Saturday night.http://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/carnage-on-the-roads-over-heritage-weekend-death-toll-over-40-20170924